<DIV align="left" style="margin-left: 0%; margin-right: 0%; text-indent: 8%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times; color: #000000; background: #FFFFFF">
    The Company&#146;s Internet website address is
    <I><U>www.merck.com</U>.</I> The Company will make available,
    free of charge at the &#147;Investor Information&#148; portion
    of its website, its Annual Report on
